{"_id":"wr5jd318i4","name":"Accurate Attack","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>When you make an accurate attack, you can take a penalty of up to –5 on the effect modifier of the attack and add the same number (up to +5) to your attack bonus.</p>","rang":1}}
{"_id":"yst456ydr9d","name":"Agile Feint","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You can use your Acrobatics bonus or movement speed rank in place of Deception to feint and trick in combat.</p>","rang":1}}
{"_id":"1fsvjcn8d36","name":"All-out Attack","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>When you make an all-out attack, you can take a penalty of up to –5 on your active defenses (Dodge and Parry) and add the same number (up to +5) to your attack bonus.</p>","rang":1}}
{"_id":"vs7b4zjgie","name":"Improved Initiative","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>+4 bonus to initiative checks per rank.</p>","rang":1}}
{"_id":"i1dxpj5tcna","name":"Iron Will","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>+2 circumstance bonus on Will resistance checks.</p>","rang":1}}
{"_id":"0qrazseqegv","name":"Great Endurance","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>+5 bonus on checks to avoid fatigue and to hold your breath.</p>","rang":1}}
{"_id":"rpgogxrcmwj","name":"Evasion","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>+2 circumstance bonus to Dodge checks to avoid area effects. Rank 2 increases bonus to +5.</p>","rang":2}}
{"_id":"hovga8kp24q","name":"Attractive","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>+2 circumstance bonus on Deception and Persuasion checks (+5 for rank 2).</p>","rang":1}}
{"_id":"2xjz86c8rt","name":"Eidetic Memory","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>Perfect recall. +5 circumstance bonus on memory checks. Can make Expertise checks as if trained.</p>","rang":1}}
{"_id":"chndwk86ybt","name":"Animal Empathy","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You have a special connection with animals. You can use interaction skills on animals normally.</p>","rang":1}}
{"_id":"ics11g2x07o","name":"Artificer","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You can use the Expertise: Magic skill to create temporary magical devices.</p>","rang":1}}
{"_id":"uuzjk94kxkg","name":"Assessment","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You can use Insight to able to judge an opponent’s relative combat capabilities.</p>","rang":1}}
{"_id":"ei1iw7v9ry","name":"Beginner's Luck","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>By spending a hero point, you gain an effective 5 ranks in a skill in which you currently have 0 ranks.</p>","rang":1}}
{"_id":"k5xdfqo8szj","name":"Benefit","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You have some significant social or structural benefit, such as wealth, status, or a secret identity.</p>","rang":1}}
{"_id":"2ouzdovbyuv","name":"Chokehold","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>If you successfully grab and maintain a hold on an opponent, you can suffocate them.</p>","rang":1}}
{"_id":"217yxzg8guk","name":"Connected","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You know people who can help you out. You can call in favors by making a Persuasion check.</p>","rang":1}}
{"_id":"p363iwof8yo","name":"Contacts","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You have extensive contacts. You can make an Investigation check to gather information in only one minute.</p>","rang":1}}
{"_id":"08lr4ibktytq","name":"Daze","type":"talent","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/talent.svg","system":{"description":"<p>You can make a Deception or Intimidation check as a standard action to cause an opponent to hesitate in combat.</p>","rang":2}}
